Aah. Oh man this is maGhribi suufiana andaaz....
soo beautiful... in Morocco, Turkey, atc they read quran in chorus of ten tewnty thirty people. and do loud hah! like that...
I just loved it... i used to go to Khutubia masjid an hour before Juma just to listen to their qirat.
 I hiked across Altas mountains into desert slept in roman ruins old masaajid...
Very cheap, safe, no crime, friendly people and Noo pollution. All organic pure food.
My next trip will be a walk across KPK Pakistan and maybe if safe into Gilgit and other mountain areas.., Inshaallah.
